4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to train students in essential technologies like JavaScript and Python over 18 weeks. This program targets aspiring developers, providing hands-on experience in building websites and apps. Key aspects include 3 weekly classes with a 1:7 teacher-student ratio, no prior coding skills required, and instruction available in English or Spanish. Students conclude the program by developing a personal project and earning a Full-Stack Developer certificate. Notable instructors include Rodolfo Campos and Gabriel Salinas, both experienced in the tech industry. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop